===Etymology 2===
The element was named after {{term|w:Pallas|Pallas}}, an [[asteroid]] that had been discovered two years before the element.
{{elements|Pd|rhodium|Rh|silver|Ag}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{element}} A metallic chemical element (''symbol'' Pd) with an [[atomic number]] of 46.

